					<description><![CDATA[I lack self belief and confidence I am writing my first novel and have written it over and over in my head to the  point of knowing every detail of the characters I&#039;ve created yet I&#039;m having such a hard time believing I can really do this.  Is it just a dream? I have no support from anyone.  Superficial friends love my ideas but when I&#039;m left alone the negative demons get their way. Chewing my confidence until all I have left is doubts. You&#039;re going to fail. You won&#039;t get it finished.  So then the frustration takes over and I fall down a great big hole. Depression. A place all to familiar where I&#039;ve wasted so much of my life.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I lack self belief and confidence I am writing my first novel and have written it over and over in my head to the  point of knowing every detail of the characters I&#8217;ve created yet I&#8217;m having such a hard time believing I can really do this.  Is it just a dream? I have no support from anyone.  Superficial friends love my ideas but when I&#8217;m left alone the negative demons get their way. Chewing my confidence until all I have left is doubts. You&#8217;re going to fail. You won&#8217;t get it finished.  So then the frustration takes over and I fall down a great big hole. Depression. A place all to familiar where I&#8217;ve wasted so much of my life.</p>
